{% block main %}
    <h1 class="ons-u-mb-s"><span class="ons-u-fs-m ons-u-db ons-u-mb-xs ons-u-lighter">Reset password</span>Check your email</h1>

    <p>We have sent an email to: <strong id="boldedEmail" class="ons-u-fs-r--b"></strong></p>
    
    <p>The email may take a few minutes to arrive. If it does not, please check your spam, bulk or junk email folder as your email system may have blocked it by mistake. </p>
        
    <p>A link to reset your password will only be sent if the email you provided is associated with an activated account. If you do not receive a link, you may need to <a href="/prototypes/example/login_journeys/CreateAccount/">create an account</a>.</p>


